dct_description_sm: Map shows the newly created lots of the Grand View property of the North Hudson Land Co., in Ridgefield Township. Officers of the company were: T. Herman Walker, president, Frederick Walker, treasurer and Henry J. Gordon, secretary. Land was divided into lots by Beyer and McCann, Civil Engineers.
